data.meta_site_name: Famous Local Food here in Philippines
data.text:
Suman is a Rice Cake originated from the Philippines,which is popular as one of the Usual snack here in Philippines specially from some provinces here in our country.It is the Rice cake snack that is non-occasional delicacy that can seen and eaten anywhere and anytime.

It is made from a Glutinous Rice (Malagkit na Bigas),Coconut Milk,White Sugar,Ginger(grated),Pinch Salt,Water for steaming,Banana Leaf.

One thing that everyone needs to know is there is a a lot of kind of Suman,Suman sa ibos,Suman sa Lihiya,Tupig,Suman Pinipig,Black Rice Suman,Suman Moron,Pintos,Suman sa Budbud,there is a lot of different kinds of Suman depending on which places it made from and what kind of Ingredients that it has been use..but alll of this are all guarantee will be worth it to taste for ..
